description:
Tired of the usual style? Make your phone unique with our brand-new themes! Every theme contains a set of hand-made icons, wallpapers, and widgets to make your phone gorgeous!


For too long, have been stuck with stock icons and could not personalize your home screen. That’s no longer! With Icon Changer, you now have the ability to customize your app icons in 100’s of different colors, themes, styles and create the perfect home screen aesthetic you’ve always dreamed of.

Inside Icon Changer you can get access to all your favourite app icons. The Shortcuts app you will not need to download. All you will need to do is download our app to start making your iPhone look like our App Store screenshots & much more!


Themes Included

-        iOS 14 Themes
-        Aesthetic Theme
-        Thanksgiving Theme
-        Neon Themes
-        Christmas Themes
-        Diwali Themes
